    "title": "Entry-Level Visual Merchandiser at PC Jeweller South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Grow your career with PC Jeweller South Asia Partners! We are hiring a Visual Merchandiser for our Gurgaon team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout PC Jeweller South Asia Partners:\nPC Jeweller South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with PC Jeweller South Asia Partners!",
